---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const updated = "2026-06-19";
---

<BaseLayout
	title="Grievance officer — PDF Tools"
	description="Mandatory contact under India's IT Rules 2021."
	canonical="/legal/grievance"
>
	<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-blue-50/30 border-b border-gray-200/60">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
			<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2">
				<a href="/" class="hover:text-gray-900">PDF Tools</a> /
				<a href="/legal/" class="hover:text-gray-900">Legal</a> / Grievance officer
			</p>
			<h1 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 tracking-tight mb-2">
				Grievance officer
			</h1>
			<p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Last updated: {updated}</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 prose prose-gray max-w-none">
		<p>
			Per the <strong>Information Technology (Intermediary Guidelines and Digital
			Media Ethics Code) Rules, 2021</strong>, the following contact handles
			complaints related to pdf.oriz.in and the broader oriz family.
		</p>

		<div class="not-prose my-6 p-6 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl">
			<p class="my-1.5"><strong>Name:</strong> Chirag Singhal</p>
			<p class="my-1.5"><strong>Designation:</strong> Grievance Officer</p>
			<p class="my-1.5"><strong>Email:</strong>
				<a href="mailto:whyiswhen@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">whyiswhen@gmail.com</a>
			</p>
			<p class="my-1.5"><strong>Address:</strong> Bhubaneswar, Odisha, India 751001</p>
			<p class="my-1.5"><strong>Response time:</strong> Acknowledgement within 24 hours; resolution within 15 days.</p>
		</div>

		<h2>What you can report</h2>
		<ul>
			<li>Content on pdf.oriz.in or other oriz sites that infringes your copyright (DMCA / Indian copyright complaints).</li>
			<li>Content that violates the IT Rules (defamation, obscenity, threats, impersonation).</li>
			<li>Privacy concerns under the DPDP Act 2023 — access, correction, deletion of your data.</li>
			<li>Account takeover or security incidents.</li>
		</ul>

		<p>
			Please include: a clear description of the issue, the URL(s) involved,
			proof you are the rights-holder (for copyright), and your contact details.
		</p>
	</article>
</BaseLayout>
